    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Consolidates the existing Checkbook NYC API (XML-first, vendor Drupal), the Comptroller's NYC Open Data assets, and the WordPress eClaim workflow behind one agent contract.",
